title: Immediately Ready Two Bed Two Bath With Up To $1000 Off Move In!
posting_body: ['Woodlake Apartments, managed by Sares-Regis Group', '11400 NE 132nd St', 'Kirkland, WA 98034', 'show contact info', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Woodlake Apartments offers a selection of one or two bedroom apartment homes to fit your lifestyle.', 'All of our apartments offer the latest features and amenities where you will be able to experience the highest levels of quality and luxury in Kirkland, Washington.', 'Lease today!', 'This two bedroom two bathroom apartment features a fully equipped kitchen, with GE stainless and black appliances, kitchen tiled backsplash, white cabinetry with contemporary pulls, and an undermounted stainless deep kitchen sink.', 'It also comes with a fireplace, mirrored closet doors, new light fixtures, smart home thermostat, USB plugs, washer/dryer, and a deck with storage!', 'Apartment Features', '* Quartz Countertops', '* GE Appliances', '* Lofty Vaulted Ceilings (on select apartments)', '* Stainless Steel Appliances', '* Private Patio or Private Balcony (on select apartments)', '* Wood Floors', '* Refrigerator, Microwave, Dishwasher & Electric Stove', '* Disposal', '* Fireplace', '* Washer and Dryer in unit', 'Monday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Tuesday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Wednesday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Thursday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Friday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Saturday 10:00am - 5:00pm', 'Sunday 12:00pm - 5:00pm', 'Community Features', '* Minutes from Restaurants, Shopping, and Much More', '* Tennis Court', '* Professionally Managed', '* After-Hours Emergency Maintenance', '* Package Acceptance', '* Basketball Court', '* Fitness Studio', '* WiFi Access', '* Renters Insurance is Required', '* Easy Access to Public Transportation', '* Swimming Pool', '* Easy Freeway Access', '* Community Lounge', '* Playground', '*', "Our prices change daily, price listed is based on today's availability.", 'Call for details.']
